event AccessControlUpdated(address target, uint8 role, bool access)
event AllyRewardDistributed(address indexed ally, address indexed trader, uint256 volumeUsd, uint256 amountToken, uint256 amountValueUsd)
event AllyRewardsClaimed(address indexed ally, uint256 amountToken)
event ReferrerRegistered(address indexed trader, address indexed referrer)
event ReferrerRewardDistributed(address indexed referrer, address indexed trader, uint256 volumeUsd, uint256 amountToken, uint256 amountValueUsd)
event ReferrerRewardsClaimed(address indexed referrer, uint256 amountToken)
event ReferrerWhitelisted(address indexed referrer, address indexed ally)
function distributeReferralReward(address _trader, uint256 _volumeUsd, uint256 _pairOpenFeeP, uint256 _tokenPriceUsd) returns (uint256)

function getAllyDetails(address _ally) view returns (tuple(address[] referrersReferred, uint256 volumeReferredUsd, uint256 pendingRewardsToken, uint256 totalRewardsToken, uint256 totalRewardsValueUsd, bool active))

function getReferrerDetails(address _referrer) view returns (tuple(address ally, address[] tradersReferred, uint256 volumeReferredUsd, uint256 pendingRewardsToken, uint256 totalRewardsToken, uint256 totalRewardsValueUsd, bool active))
